data.description:
Modern watchface with design inspired by flightboard and GRID watchface, with deep focus on usability\battery savings:
-Screen-optimized font with good readability;
-Thrifty battery usage: only necessary updates per minute, no useless startup animation;
-BT disconnect alert with vibes and popup;
-Doesn't show battery alerts since the system does it already.

Hope you'll like RUZN.

Watchface in style gta:
+ Style - monochrome, gta3, san andreas, vice city (after the change of the style, you must restart the whatchface);
+ Time - current time; 
+ Health - pebble battery and step counter;
+ Money - current date or manual text (numbers) or step counter; 
+ Stars - current week day (from monday to friday) or bluetooth connection state (where 1 and 5 - double vibration); 
+ Status pebble battery charging; 
+ The date format change; 
+ Changing weapons, depends on the day of the week;
+ Pebble Health;
+ "Settings" button.
